name: Room near MBTA Forest Hills, keyless self check-in
neighborhood_overview: Arnold Arboretum is only a few minute walk, pizza store like Domino's is nearby. Target and supermarkets are less than 1 mile away.
description:
Great location, conveniently located just steps away from Washington St in Roslindale, where 8 bus routes pass, only 4 bus stops to Forest Hills T Station. Walk to Arnold Arboretum.
Private room in the Boston neighborhood of Roslindale, it comes with a queen size bed, hardwood floor.
Newly renovated large kitchen with dining area, coin-operated laundry in Basement.
Keyless self check-in for your convenience.
Also enjoy fast Gig speed Internet in the house.

The space
This room is on the first floor of a smoke-free/ pet-free two-family house.
Shared kitchen and bathroom, coin-operated laundry in the basement.
